title: Record of Agarest War NTSC/U NTSC/J Xbox 360
description:
Record of Agarest War:

Region      : NTSC/U NTSC/J (Excludes China) Languages: English        
Size        : 1 DVD                          Genre    : RPG 
Platform    : XBOX 360                       Date     : 4/2010

About:

Prepare yourself for an adventure so big, it takes more than one generation to experience it. The world of Agarest is once again the battleground between the forces of Dark and Light. Choose the path of Light or Darkness, then watch your in-game actions shape the future as you play through a massive 100-hour-plus storyline. Hand-pick your group of warriors and fight hundreds of different enemies. Check the Affection Gauge to get a quick read on where you stand with the game's many ladies. Take the hand of a worthy bride and use the Soul Breed System to give birth to a new hero and spawn an all-new adventure.
